{"tid":135148,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大學理科不如工程，工程一定要港大","createTime":"2017-02-26T06:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T01:53:39.000Z","uid":14170,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b776977d2484979ba66c38d1c5a161c70128d9c1","tid":135148,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"1. 夠 hea<br />\n雖然 HKU 每科既內容都係其他學校 1.5 倍，但係絕大部分科目只有一個 Lab，分分鐘連 mid term test 都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSem 頭中去哂玩，留最後一個月爆書都夠過 3 有突 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：起碼走七成堂，自己讀照 A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 自由<br />\n上面講左，HKU 課程係又多又深 (同其他 U 比)，但係 HKU 從來唔會逼你讀書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你鐘意走堂打機，上莊，溝女，摺 lib，做乜鳩都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔讀書咪 C Range 囉，HKU 唔會肥你，但係畢業搵工自己受返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想讀書咪跟每個 course 既 material 去搵書學，好多時班教授第一堂已經講有咩 ref. book，即係叫你唔洗上堂啦，自己讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣讀出黎絕對唔會差過 UST 班書蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你讀書讀得勁過大陸班省狀元既時候，亞洲仲邊有人夠你爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 歷史<br />\n當你出去返工，你班上司有一日撩你傾計問你咩 hall，然後佢講佢當年打 interhall 既盛況，你又講下依家間 hall 變成點，傾到有講有笑個陣，你就知咩叫 百年學府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：試過返 DSE 工，個試場主任本來串柒柒，有日知道我係 HKU 學生後佢自爆係 Swire 老鬼，然後成日買野我食，放工又車我走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516e4256fcf88f428fb7420c8a9947c07f401d14","tid":135148,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"4. 名牌<br />\n我唔係指係香港對住班師奶咁做，而係當你去外地 exchange，外地班老師同同學都會識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你創造更多機會<br />\n係日本：HKU &gt; UTokyo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係香港：HKU = 畢業 12k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576d56e155fcd9204d82acee30cea9d8ff5613e5","tid":135148,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4. 名牌<br />\n我唔係指係香港對住班師奶咁做，而係當你去外地 exchange，外地班老師同同學都會識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你創造更多機會<br />\n係日本：HKU &gt; UTokyo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係香港：HKU = 畢業 12k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東大 exchange partners 只有 HKU CU <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aad3e993c8b329a3c1f4fa29ea001cf803fea2b","tid":135148,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87f506460c6d6f690700c2c5de45f12641acac95","tid":135148,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CU KongU 萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCIVIL 起薪 22k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c238f49d67617746d2f7669a2b2672763c6cfb","tid":135148,"uid":7